LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:微分方程：双曲型：多波：解耦"

\end_inset

 的过程中，用到了“
\begin_inset Formula $\Matrix{L}$
\end_inset

 及 
\begin_inset Formula $\Matrix{R}$
\end_inset

 都是常数矩阵”，它是“
\begin_inset Formula $\Matrix{A}$
\end_inset

 为常数矩阵”的推论。若将 
\begin_inset Formula $\Matrix{A}$
\end_inset

 放宽为“显式依赖于 
\begin_inset Formula $x,t$
\end_inset

 的方阵”：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\partial_{t}+\Matrix{A(x,t)}\partial_{x}\right)\ket{U}=\ket{0}
\]

\end_inset

则 
\begin_inset Formula $\Matrix{A(x,t)}$
\end_inset

 的特征值 
\begin_inset Formula $\Matrix{\lambda(x,t)}$
\end_inset

 需要逐点计算，方程的双曲性也要逐点分析。即使方程是处处双曲的，
\begin_inset Formula $\Matrix{L(x,t)}$
\end_inset

 也不再是常数矩阵，将其与算符 
\begin_inset Formula $\partial_{t}$
\end_inset

 及 
\begin_inset Formula $\partial_{x}$
\end_inset

 交换顺序会产生（不含 
\begin_inset Formula $\partial_{t}\ket{U}$
\end_inset

 或 
\begin_inset Formula $\partial_{x}\ket{U}$
\end_inset

 的）附加项：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Matrix{L}\partial_{\alpha}\ket{U}=\partial_{\alpha}\left(\Matrix{L}\ket{U}\right)-\left(\partial_{\alpha}\Matrix{L}\right)\ket{U}\qquad\alpha\in\left\{ t,x\right\} 
\]

\end_inset

因此，变系数线性一阶方程组至多可以对一阶导数解耦：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}\left(\partial_{t}+\Matrix{A}\partial_{x}\right)\ket{U} & =\Matrix{R}\cdot\left(\Matrix{L}\partial_{t}+\Matrix{\Lambda}\Matrix{L}\partial_{x}\right)\ket{U}\\
 & =\Matrix{R}\cdot\left(\partial_{t}+\Matrix{\Lambda}\partial_{x}\right)\Matrix{L}\ket{U}-\Matrix{R}\cdot\left(\partial_{t}\Matrix{L}+\Matrix{\Lambda}\partial_{x}\Matrix{L}\right)\ket{U}
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset

即一阶非齐次方程组
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\partial_{t}+\Matrix{\Lambda}\partial_{x}\right)\ket{V}=\underbrace{\left(\partial_{t}\Matrix{L}+\Matrix{\Lambda}\partial_{x}\Matrix{L}\right)\Matrix{R}}_{\Matrix{D}}\ket{V}
\]

\end_inset

其中 
\begin_inset Formula $\Matrix{D}$
\end_inset

 是只依赖于 
\begin_inset Formula $\Matrix{A}$
\end_inset

 的变系数矩阵。
\end_layout

